SELECT "n"."transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY EXTRACT(DAY FROM "day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "a" FROM "transactions") AS "n" WHERE "n"."a"=1 ORDER BY "n"."transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" WHERE ROW(DATE("day"),"amount") IN (SELECT DATE("day") AS "d",MAX("amount") FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY "d") ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT DATE("day") AS "day","transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "Transactions") AS "a" WHERE "rnk"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "T"."transaction_id" FROM (SELECT *,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "RNK" FROM "Transactions") AS "T" WHERE "RNK"=1 ORDER BY 1

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT EXTRACT(DAY FROM "day") AS "d",MAX("amount") AS "max_amount" FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY EXTRACT(DAY FROM "day")) SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" JOIN "cte" ON EXTRACT(DAY FROM "day")="d" WHERE "amount"="max_amount" ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" AS "t" WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM "Transactions" AS "t1" WHERE DATE("t1"."day")=DATE("t"."day") AND "t1"."amount">"t"."amount") ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "temp" AS (SELECT DATE("day") AS "dt",MAX("amount") AS "amt" FROM "transactions" GROUP BY 1) SELECT "t"."transaction_id" FROM "transactions" AS "t" JOIN "temp" ON DATE("t"."day")="temp"."dt" AND "t"."amount"="temp"."amt" ORDER BY 1

WITH "trans1" AS (SELECT "transaction_id",DATE("day") AS "day",MAX("amount") OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day")) AS "maxi",DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "ranking" FROM "transactions") SELECT DISTINCT "a"."transaction_id" FROM "transactions" AS "a" JOIN "trans1" AS "b" ON "a"."transaction_id"="b"."transaction_id" WHERE "a"."amount"="b"."maxi" AND "ranking"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" WHERE ROW("amount",CAST("day" AS DATE)) IN (SELECT MAX("amount"),CAST("day" AS DATE) FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY CAST("day" AS DATE)) ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM ("transactions" AS "tr") JOIN (SELECT LEFT("day", 10) AS "day",MAX("amount") AS "amount" FROM "transactions" GROUP BY LEFT("day", 10)) AS "t" WHERE LEFT("tr"."day", 10)="t"."day" AND "tr"."amount"="t"."amount" ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "transaction_id","amount",MAX("amount") OVER (PARTITION BY EXTRACT(DAY FROM "day")) AS "max_amount" FROM "Transactions") SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "cte" WHERE "amount"="max_amount" ORDER BY 1
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "Transactions") AS "temp1" WHERE "rnk"=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "ranked" FROM "transactions") AS "f" WHERE "ranked"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "t"."transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY CAST("day" AS DATE) ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "transactions") AS "t" WHERE "t"."rnk"=1 ORDER BY "t"."transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "Transactions") AS "Temp" WHERE "rnk"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "transactions" WHERE ROW(DATE("day"),"amount") IN (SELECT DATE("day") AS "day",MAX("amount") AS "max_amt" FROM "transactions" GROUP BY 1) ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT *,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "day" ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rn" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",SUBSTR("day", 1, 10) AS "day","amount" FROM "transactions") AS "tb1") AS "tb2" WHERE "rn"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" AS "T" LEFT JOIN (SELECT DATE("day") AS "date",MAX("amount") AS "amount" FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY "date") AS "M" ON DATE("T"."day")="M"."date" WHERE "T"."amount"="M"."amount" ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",DATE("day") AS "day","amount",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "ranks" FROM "Transactions") AS "a" WHERE "ranks"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "z"."transaction_id" FROM (SELECT *,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rk" FROM "transactions") AS "z" WHERE "z"."rk"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" AS "t" JOIN (SELECT DATE("day") AS "day",MAX("amount") AS "amount" FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY DATE("day")) AS "max_t" ON DATE("t"."day")="max_t"."day" AND "t"."amount"="max_t"."amount" ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "cte1" AS (SELECT "transaction_id",TO_CHAR("day", 'YYYY-%m-%d') AS "day","amount" FROM "transactions"), "cte2" AS (SELECT "transaction_id","amount",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "day" ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "ranking" FROM "cte1") SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "cte2" WHERE "ranking"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT *,RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "RNK" FROM "transactions") AS "A" WHERE "RNK"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT DISTINCT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" AS "a" WHERE "amount"=(SELECT MAX("amount") FROM "Transactions" AS "b" WHERE DATE("a"."day")=DATE("b"."day")) ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rn" FROM "Transactions") AS "temp" WHERE "rn"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id","dt",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "dt" ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",DATE("day") AS "dt","amount" FROM "Transactions") AS "a") AS "b" WHERE "rnk"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "tmp" AS (SELECT "transaction_id","day","amount",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY DATE("day") ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "ranks" FROM "Transactions") SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "tmp" WHERE "ranks"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "t1"."transaction_id",TO_CHAR("t1"."day", 'YYYY-%m-%d'),COUNT(DISTINCT "t2"."amount") AS "ct" FROM "transactions" AS "t1" LEFT JOIN "transactions" AS "t2" ON TO_CHAR("t1"."day", 'YYYY-%m-%d')=TO_CHAR("t2"."day", 'YYYY-%m-%d') AND "t1"."amount"<"t2"."amount" GROUP BY "t1"."transaction_id",TO_CHAR("t1"."day", 'YYYY-%m-%d')) AS "a" WHERE "ct"=0

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY CAST("day" AS DATE) ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "Transactions") AS "t" WHERE "t"."rnk"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"
SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "transactions" WHERE ROW(DATE("day"),"amount") IN (SELECT DATE("day"),MAX("amount") FROM "transactions" GROUP BY DATE("day")) ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "tmp" AS (SELECT "transaction_id",CAST("day" AS DATE) AS "day","amount",MAX("amount") OVER (PARTITION BY CAST("day" AS DATE)) AS "day_max" FROM "Transactions") SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "tmp" WHERE "amount"="day_max" ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "t1"."transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" AS "t1" JOIN (SELECT TO_CHAR("day", 'YYYY-%m-%d') AS "date",MAX("amount") AS "amt" FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY TO_CHAR("day", 'YYYY-%m-%d')) AS "t2" ON TO_CHAR("t1"."day", 'YYYY-%m-%d')="t2"."date" AND "amount"="amt" ORDER BY "t1"."transaction_id"

SELECT "t"."transaction_id" FROM "transactions" AS "t" WHERE "t"."amount"=(SELECT MAX("tt"."amount") FROM "transactions" AS "tt" WHERE EXTRACT(DAY FROM "tt"."day")=EXTRACT(DAY FROM "t"."day")) ORDER BY "t"."transaction_id"
WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "transaction_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY LEFT("day", 10) ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "rk" FROM "transactions" ORDER BY 1) SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "cte" WHERE "rk"=1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "Transactions" LEFT JOIN (SELECT MAX("amount") AS "max_amount","day" FROM "Transactions" GROUP BY TO_CHAR("day", 'YYYY, %M, dd')) AS "t" ON "t"."max_amount"="Transactions"."amount" AND TO_CHAR("t"."day", 'YYYY, %M, dd')=TO_CHAR("Transactions"."day", 'YYYY, %M, dd') WHERE "max_amount" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "transaction_id"

WITH "tb1" AS (SELECT "transaction_id",LEFT("day", POSITION(' ' IN "day")-1) AS "day_date","amount" FROM "Transactions"), "tb2" AS (SELECT "transaction_id","day_date",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "day_date" ORDER BY "amount" DESC) AS "amount_rank" FROM "tb1") SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "tb2" WHERE "amount_rank"=1 ORDER BY "transaction_id"

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM "transactions" AS "trans" JOIN (SELECT DATE("day") AS "day",MAX("amount") AS "max_amt" FROM "transactions" GROUP BY 1) AS "t" ON DATE("trans"."day")="t"."day" AND "trans"."amount"="t"."max_amt" ORDER BY 1

SELECT "transaction_id" FROM (SELECT "transaction_id","amount",MAX("amount") OVER (PARTITION BY TO_CHAR("day", 'YYYY-%m-%d')) AS "mm" FROM "Transactions") AS "TEMP" WHERE "amount"="mm" ORDER BY "transaction_id"
